summary: HomeDashBoardWhitePaper - A social experiment of absolute fairness, without dumping, filled with free play! $NONO is a reward-based meme token that aims to maintain absolute fairness and make memes more interesting. Token total supply is 21,000 with liquidity at 100% and a tax of 10% (7.5% pool, 2.5% marketing). The contract address is 0x9BeC7A0BafeeaD2eAAEf71c7e0Ee8EaDe0E6b33c. The project values transparency and will disclose all information about $NONO before launch. There is no detailed roadmap as all outcomes are participant-driven.
